Ubuntu packages needed to compile bloodspilot2:

make
gcc
libc6-dev
zlib1g-dev (optional)
libx11-dev
libxxf86misc-dev (optional)

libsdl-dev           (unless configuring with --disable-sdl-client)
libsdl-ttf2.0-dev    (unless configuring with --disable-sdl-client)
libsdl-image1.2-dev  (unless configuring with --disable-sdl-client)

Useful for development:

automake1.9
autoconf